      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze these WhatsApp messages and create a prioritized to-do list.\n\nExtract:\n- Tasks and action items\n- Important deadlines\n- Follow-ups needed\n- Commitments made\n\nMessages:\n{{ $json.allMessages }}\n\nCreate a to-do list organized by:\nüî¥ HIGH PRIORITY\nüü° MEDIUM PRIORITY\nüü¢ LOW PRIORITY\n\nBe concise and actionable.",
